hudson.model.StringParameterValue.name: fdcenv
hudson.model.StringParameterValue.description: Choose the environment you want to deploy to.

hudson.model.StringParameterValue.name: Git_branch
hudson.model.StringParameterValue.description: Please mention required git branch Eg: develop release/xxxx.xx.xx

org.jenkinsci.plugins.pipeline.modeldefi.value: ImageTag=$(grep -A1 "ImageTag" ${WORKSPACE}/fdc-svc-api-${fdcenv}-parameter.json | tail -1 | cut -d ":" -f2 | cut -d "\"" -f2) if [ $releaseVersion = "latest" ] then sed -i "s/$ImageTag/${dockerTag}/" ${WORKSPACE}/fdc-svc-api-${fdcenv}-parameter.json else sed -i "s/$ImageTag/${releaseVersion}/" ${WORKSPACE}/fdc-svc-api-${fdcenv}-parameter.json fi
